OL,3,CMore than 70,000 instances of abuse in
OL,4,Cfive years towards healthcare staff
OL,6,FIt's not just the pressure of dealing
OL,7,Fwith large numbers of patients; staff
OL,8,Fare also facing a very real risk of
OL,9,Fabuse while trying to do their job.
OL,11,FUTV learned on Monday, as hospitals
OL,12,Fstruggled to find space for new
OL,13,Fpatients, there was an attempt to
OL,14,Fstrangle a healthcare worker in Daisy
OL,15,FHill Emergency Department.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Southern Health
OL,18,FTrust said: "The incident was
OL,19,Funderstandably hugely distressing for
OL,20,Fthe member of staff and that the
OL,21,Fappropriate support is being provided."
