OL,3,CMore than 70,000 instances of abuse in
OL,4,Cfive years towards healthcare staff
OL,6,FThe Trust added: "Our staff work
OL,7,Fextremely hard in challenging and
OL,8,Fpressurised conditions to care for
OL,9,Fpatients, and attacks on them are not
OL,10,Ftolerated."
OL,12,FThe matter is currently under PSNI
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FStatistics obtained by Health
OL,16,FCommittee member Diane Dodds are
OL,17,Fshocking: 60,000 physical attacks on
OL,18,FHealth Trust staff over the last five
OL,19,Fyears, and 12,000 incidents of verbal
OL,20,Fabuse.
