OL,3,CMore than 70,000 instances of abuse in
OL,4,Cfive years towards healthcare staff
OL,6,FDiane Dodds MLA said: "It's utterly,
OL,7,Futterly appalling. Imagine the anxiety
OL,8,Fof going into your work, going into a
OL,9,Fworkplace where you are there to help
OL,10,Fpeople at their sickest and most
OL,11,Fvulnerable, and you could be subject
OL,12,Fto these kind of attacks."
OL,14,FThe Royal College of Nursing said that
OL,15,Fthe level of abuse has become so bad
OL,16,Fthat some staff feel afraid going into
OL,17,Fthe workplace, and has called on the
OL,18,FJustice Minister to introduce tougher
OL,19,Fsentences.
