OL,3,CMore than 70,000 instances of abuse in
OL,4,Cfive years towards healthcare staff
OL,6,F"It should be a never event in any
OL,7,Fhealthcare setting that any nurse or
OL,8,Fhealthcare worker is assaulted at the
OL,9,Ftime when they're delivering care."
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Health Minister
OL,12,Fsaid: "Violence and aggression towards
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care staff are
OL,14,Fcompletely unacceptable and will not
OL,15,Fbe tolerated."
OL,17,FHe added: "Every member of staff has
OL,18,Fthe right to feel safe and respected
OL,19,Fat work, and we will continue to take
OL,20,Fall necessary steps to protect and
OL,21,Fsupport our workforce."
